'''2013年沃克斯豪爾直升機墜毀事件'''是指在2013年1月16日[[格林威治標準時間|格林威治標準時間]]7時59分，一架[[直升機|直升機]]在[[倫敦|倫敦]][[沃克斯豪爾|沃克斯豪爾]]撞到{{Link-en|聖喬治碼頭大廈|St George Wharf Tower}}的建築[[起重機|起重機]]懸臂後墜毀<ref name=GuardLive>{{cite news|title=Vauxhall helicopter crash leaves two dead: latest news from London|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/jan/16/helicopter-crash-in-vauxhall-live-updates|accessdate=2013-01-17|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2013-01-16|archive-date=2013-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526170947/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/jan/16/helicopter-crash-in-vauxhall-live-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=DMail2263213>{{cite news|title=Two killed and at least 11 injured as helicopter crashes into crane on new Thames-side skyscraper and plunges into rush-hour traffic|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2263213/Helicopter-crash-Vauxhall-central-London-2-killed-2-injured-helicopter-hits-Thames-skyscraper.html|accessdate=2013-01-16|newspaper=Daily Mail|date=2013-01-16|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911233659/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2263213/Vauxhall-Helicopter-crash-Matthew-Wood-named-second-victim-pilot-Pete-Barnes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，造成50歲的飛行員{{Link-en|彼得·巴恩斯 (飛行員)|Peter Barnes (pilot)|彼得·巴恩斯}}和另一名39歲行人馬修·伍德（Matthew Wood）逝世<ref name=GuardLive/><ref name=BBC21041468>{{cite news|title=London helicopter crash: Two die in Vauxhall crane accident|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-21040410|accessdate=2013-03-24|newspaper=BBC Online|date=2013-01-16|archive-date=2013-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130326214320/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-21040410|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=BBC21087595>{{cite news|title=London helicopter crash victim Matthew Wood killed in fire|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21087595|accessdate=2013-01-18|newspaper=BBC website|date=2013-01-18|archive-date=2013-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130118185344/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21087595|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在這次[[空難|空難]]中還造成5人被送往醫院，另外有7人則是在現場受到波及而必須醫治<ref name=BBC21041468/>。

